<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hun puikhawm un mun a um nalai,
 Lalpen guolvak bawlna achun;
 Aw, hun puikhawm un, A In hung dim hen,
 Mi gimthei, gilkiel te'n um hen.

[V2]
 Lam lien leh lam neu ah chieh unla,
 Gitlohna lampi thim lak ah;
 Chieh un chieh un hehpih lunggil pu'n,
 Vakvaite hun pui lut un.

[V3]
 2. Hun pui khawm un, mun a um na lai,
 Mahleh chielna limsak lote;
 I ngaihtuoh in lunggil a suna ngei,
 Sapna za kit ding ei ta puou!

[V4]
 3. Hun puikhawm un, mun a um na lai,
 Chung Pathien thuvaithak ahi;
 Aw, zahngaihna huongah hun pui lut un,
 Hukdampa hehpihna khutah.

[V5]
 4. Lungngai, liengvai leh hausate di'n,
 Thangvan akhun mun a um ie;
 Aw hun puikhawm un, kawt kikhak ma hin,
 Gunchuh takin hilhviel un la.

[V6]
 5. Van guolvakna dak gi ding ei tai,
 Gam thiengtho hung tun ding ziekin;
 Lei hi lungkham, mau, kiel in a buoi tai,
 Hungun, ei unle chiel hitiu.

[V7]
 Kawt kikhak man hung kisa zo un,
 Kiel, lungkham, mau vakvaite haw;
 A Lalpau chielna thu chuh hilh in,
 Van ah um din chiel hitiu.</lyrics>
<title>GATHER THEM IN</title>
</song>